    "encrypted": "false",
    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Recreate This Timeline\r\n\r\nChloe is working with another artist to create a new song. Her job is to make the beginning portion of the song before the beat drops. Her partner gave her this timeline to recreate:\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/41449167c6868065c171234b4507e788-image-1741889152965.05.48 AM.png)\r\n\r\nTo keep her code clean and focused, Chloe wants to simplify by focusing only on the essential sounds that build the mood before the beat drops.\r\n\r\n**Your task:** Use **abstraction** to focus on the key sounds from the timeline - those that shape the atmosphere of the intro. Use the sounds you have been given and code a song that matches the timeline below.",
